End Sub

Sub Review(vmod)
    On Error Resume Next
    Set wnd = ActiveWindow
    Set sel = Selection
    wnd.View.SeekView = vmod
    rval = False
    sel.WholeStory
    hm = False
    sel.Font.Hidden = hm
    rval = True
    If rval = True Then
        sel.Collapse
    End If
End Sub

Sub ViewContent()
    Mode = 10
    Do Until Mode < 0
        Review (Mode)
        Mode = Mode - 1
    Loop
End Sub
